s &amp; Co. rendering the requisite fairness opinion. As I reported at the =
time, at least Ari didn=E2=80=99t receive a bonus for <i>this </i>asset sal=
e. <br/><br/>But an even <i>more</i> curious deal was announced on Monday: =
